A project to create a web version of the g2system. More details soon...

This is a django project to manage the processing lines of the G2System.

The code is organized in 3 apps:

- systemsettings

  Holds most of the settings for the packages, files, hosts, ... used in the 
  g2system.

- inspiresettings

  Has settings which are relevant for the metadata generation

- operations

  Has the main code for the processing lines.

There are other bits of code that concerning other parts of the system:

- extra code

  Extra algorithms that perform the product generation and other settings. 
  Some of this code is not included in the git repository, for copyright
  reasons.

- apache

  Sample configuration for the web server.

- scripts

  Scripts to be run in SMS
